<img width="107" height="107" src="https://i0.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/BBNaija-pic-107x107.jpg?resize=107%2C107&amp;ssl=1" alt="When Darling hosted ex-Big brother housemates" class="amp-wp-295b586"> Darling Nigeria, the official hair sponsor of the 2019 Big Brother Naija (BBN) show played hosts to some ex-BBN housemates; Mercy, Mike, Frodd, Omasola, Seyi, Ike, Elozonam, Diane, Sir Dee, Kim Oprah, Thelma, Cindy, Avala, Khafi, Jackye, Gedoni, Enkay and Joe, who visited the Lagos offices of the hair extension giant in appreciation of their role in keeping housemates well-groomed with their latest hair extensions and spicy hairstyles. The visit also served as an opportunity for Venita Akpofure (represented by Mercy) and Sir Dee to redeem their cheques of 500,000 naira each as winners of the Darling task while in the house. Continue reading When Darling hosted ex-Big brother housemates at Vanguard News. Source: Vanguard